data.description: Create lasting memories in this move-in ready Stone Mountain gem nestled in a well-established neighborhood. Welcome to this beautifully renovated home with fresh interior and exterior paint, new garage doors, new flooring, new HVAC, new gutters, and updated kitchen and bathrooms. You will immediately notice the spacious living room with new luxury vinyl plank that opens to the dining area with on-trend chandelier. Relax fireside in the family room by the newly painted gas fireplace. Enjoy cooking your favorite meals in the light and bright kitchen with granite countertops, white subway tile backsplash, stainless fixtures, new Samsung stainless appliances including dishwasher, electric oven range, and built-in microwave. Retreat upstairs to the primary suite, complete with a spacious bedroom, closet, and a beautifully appointed en-suite bathroom. The two secondary bedrooms with new lighting share an updated bathroom with vanity, new hardware, lighting, and mirror. Relax or entertain on the new deck perfect for grilling and enjoy the large flat yard. In the garage you will find the laundry room. No HOA, close proximity to parks, shopping and restaurants along with the convenient location close to I-285 and Marta, complete the attributes that make this your must have home. A life beyond your wildest dreams awaits you with this brand, where you can plant your roots and create lasting memories for years to come. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of modern living in a serene and peaceful setting.
